### Crypto Maps

1. ACL - Match interesting traffic
2. Policy - Phase 1 Algorithms
3. Key - Preshare Key
4. Transform-Set - Phase 2 Algorithms
5. Crypto Map - Tie everything together
6. Interface - Apply to interface

<br>

~~~
!@PNB-A
conf t
 no ip access-list extended VPN-TRAFFIC
 ip access-list extended VPN-TRAFFIC
  permit ip host 192.168.1.1 host 192.168.1.2
 !
 crypto isakmp policy 1
  encryption aes 256
  hash sha256
  group 14
  authentication pre-share
  lifetime 60
 !
 crypto isakmp key C1sc0123 address 10.1.1.5
 !
 crypto ipsec transform-set TS1 esp-aes 256 esp-sha256-hmac
  mode tunnel
 !
 crypto map PNB-VPN 1 ipsec-isakmp
  set peer 10.1.1.5
  set transform-set TS1
  match address VPN-TRAFFIC
 !
 int e1/1
  crypto map PNB-VPN
  end
~~~

